{
  "chapter": 90,
  "chapter_summary": "第九十回\"蛇足\"是多情剑客无情剑的尾声章节。李寻欢与孙小红在长亭话别，谈论胜利后的寂寞与奋斗的意义。一对无名少年少女在长亭依依惜别，少年立志要在兵器谱上成名，少女含泪等待。阿飞出现，告诉孙小红林诗音不会来了。回忆中龙小云想为父龙啸云正名，林诗音劝阻，认为龙啸云已用血洗清了一切。最后阿飞与李寻欢、孙小红告别，约定三年后回来喝喜酒。李寻欢以\"喜酒太贵\"的妙语收束全篇——请人喝喜酒意味着一辈子慢慢付账，但他偏偏不愿令朋友失望。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "一个人胜利之后，总会觉得很疲倦、很寂寞的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "因为他已经完全胜利，完全成功了，已没有什么事好再让他去奋斗的，一个失败了的人精神反而会振作些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这么样说来，成功的滋味岂非也不好受？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "虽然也不太好受，但至少总比失败好得多。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nan",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "送到这里就行了，你回去吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_shao_nan",
      "text": "你什么时候回来呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nan",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "不知道，也许一两年，也许……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_shao_nan",
      "text": "你为什么要我等这么久？为什么一定要走？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nan",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "我早就说过，我要找到那些人，将他们击败！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nan",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "那些在兵器谱上列名的人，上官金虹、李寻欢、郭嵩阳、吕凤先……我要让他们知道，我比他们更强，然后……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_shao_nan",
      "text": "然后怎么样？我们现在已经很快乐了，你将他们击败后，我们难道会更快乐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nan",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "也许不会，可是我一定要去做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_shao_nan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nan",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "因为我不能就像这样默默无闻地过一辈子，我一定要成名，要像上官金虹和李寻欢那样有名，而且我一定能做到！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_shao_nan",
      "text": "我知道你一定能做到的，无论你要去多久，我都等你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这少年若知道上官金虹的结局，只怕就不会离开他的情人了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他想和你一样有名，可是你……你是不是就比他快乐？我想……你若是他，一定就不会像他这么样做的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我若是他，也会这么样去做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你？……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "人活着，就要有理想、有目的，就要不顾一切去奋斗，至于奋斗的结果是不是成功，是不是快乐，他们并没有放在心上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有些人也许会认为这种人傻，但世上若没有这种人，这世界早就不知变成什么样子了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想她一定不会来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "她跟我约好，一定会来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她不会来！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为她自己也知道，她已不必来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "你为什么不让我去见他最后一次？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你为什么还要去见他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "text": "我至少要让他知道，我父亲是为了什么死的。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这么样做，只因为他自己觉得应该这么样做，并不是要求别人原谅，也并不是想要别人知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_shi_yin",
      "speaker_name": "林诗音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不但为自己洗清了债，也为我们还清了债，只要我们能好好地活下去，他在九泉之下也就瞑目了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三年后，我一定会回来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我回来的时候，你们当然要请我喝酒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "当然，只可惜三年未免太长了些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要喝的那种酒很特别，不知道你们肯不肯请？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你要喝什么酒？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喜酒。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我什么酒都喝过，就是没喝过喜酒，只希望你们莫要令我失望。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我什么酒都请人喝过，就是从未请人喝过喜酒，你可知道为了什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "因为喜酒太贵了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "太贵？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "因为一个男人若要请人喝喜酒，那就表示他一辈子都得慢慢地来付这笔账，只可惜我又偏偏不愿令朋友失望。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 90,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    }
  ],
